Introduction

Kim Jin-ha, better known as JinHa, is a South Korean singer formely under TR Entertainment. She is a former member of the girl group TRI.BE.

On May 31, 2022, her company announced that she would be taking a break from activities due to health issues. However, on July 21, 2023, she officially departed the group.
